SUMMARY:Super Dropper
LOCATION:London
DESCRIPTION:Super Dropper is a one-woman comedy show inspired by juggling. 
 Irreverent\, cheeky and flirtatious\, Super Dropper is passionate about jug
 gling! Thanks to her juggling props\, she expresses her weirdest philosophi
 cal thoughts and fantasies without filters. She sees the world falling apar
 t and she really wants to fix it! Her plan? Spreading the juggling love to 
 save the world. The sky is her limit! Super Dropper mixes comedy and circus
 . Halfway between autobiography and fiction\, Super Dropper explores with a
  French touch the themes of failure\, introspection and politics. Expect pu
 ns\, wit and speaking balls!\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atl
 as/event/super-dropper/
